          "date": "2015-10-07 18:11:10.000000000",
          "tz": -300
        },
        "subject": "LU-5125 lu: weaken assertion in lu_object_attr()",
        "message": "LU-5125 lu: weaken assertion in lu_object_attr()\n\nIn lu_object_attr() assert that the object exists or is remote rather\nthan just exists. In the OSP layer the exists flag may be cleared by\ncertain operations and there is no locking to make it safe for other\nthreads to use lu_object_attr() even if they first check that the\nobject exists.\n\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I5777d16e4e72ac2080a01e38adca2eaba03fd8b7\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
